To maintain and develop positive business relationships with a customer's key personnel involved in logistics activities, consistently engage in open and proactive communication, understand their business needs and challenges, provide timely and effective solutions, and seek regular feedback for continuous improvement. Schedule regular meetings or check-ins, offer value-added insights, and ensure transparency in all logistics operations. Building trust and demonstrating reliability will foster long-term partnerships and mutual success.
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
